// â”€â”€ DASHBOARD â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
// â”€â”€ WALK HEALTH GAUGE (style Apple Watch) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
const WalkHealthGauge = ({score=85}) => {
  const color = score >= 75 ? "#22C55E" : score >= 25 ? "#F97316" : "#EF4444";
  const label = score >= 75 ? "Excellent" : score >= 25 ? "Ã€ surveiller" : "Anomalie";

  // Semi-cercle SVG â€” arc de 180Â° (de 180Â° Ã  360Â°, bas gauche â†’ bas droite via le haut)
  const CX = 120, CY = 110, R = 88;
  // Arc semi-circulaire : start = gauche (-180Â°), end = droite (0Â°)
  // strokeDashoffset pour animer
  const semicircle = Math.PI * R;  // demi-pÃ©rimÃ¨tre
  const filled = semicircle * (score / 100);

  // Segments de couleur pour le fond dÃ©gradÃ© (rouge â†’ orange â†’ vert)
  const segments = [
    {pct:0.33, color:"#EF4444"},
    {pct:0.33, color:"#F97316"},
    {pct:0.34, color:"#22C55E"},
  ];

  const arcPath = (startPct, endPct) => {
    const startAngle = Math.PI + Math.PI * startPct;
    const endAngle   = Math.PI + Math.PI * endPct;
    const x1 = CX + R * Math.cos(startAngle);
    const y1 = CY + R * Math.sin(startAngle);
    const x2 = CX + R * Math.cos(endAngle);
    const y2 = CY + R * Math.sin(endAngle);
    return `M ${x1} ${y1} A ${R} ${R} 0 0 1 ${x2} ${y2}`;
  };

  // Aiguille
  const needleAngle = Math.PI + Math.PI * (score / 100);
  const nx = CX + (R - 10) * Math.cos(needleAngle);
  const ny = CY + (R - 10) * Math.sin(needleAngle);

  return (
    <div style={{display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",alignItems:"center"}}>
      <svg width={240} height={140} viewBox="0 0 240 140">

        {/* Fond gris track semi-circulaire */}
        <path d={arcPath(0,1)} fill="none" stroke="#E8ECF2" strokeWidth={18} strokeLinecap="round"/>

        {/* Segments colorÃ©s fond */}
        {segments.map((s,i)=>{
          const start = segments.slice(0,i).reduce((a,x)=>a+x.pct,0);
          return <path key={i} d={arcPath(start,start+s.pct)} fill="none"
            stroke={s.color} strokeWidth={18} strokeLinecap="butt" opacity={0.25}/>;
        })}

        {/* Arc de progression colorÃ© */}
        <path d={arcPath(0, score/100)} fill="none"
          stroke={color} strokeWidth={18} strokeLinecap="round"
          style={{transition:"all .8s ease"}}/>

        {/* Graduations */}
        {[0,25,50,75,100].map(v=>{
          const a = Math.PI + Math.PI*(v/100);
          const x1 = CX + (R+4)*Math.cos(a), y1 = CY + (R+4)*Math.sin(a);
          const x2 = CX + (R+12)*Math.cos(a), y2 = CY + (R+12)*Math.sin(a);
          return <line key={v} x1={x1} y1={y1} x2={x2} y2={y2}
            stroke="#C8D4E8" strokeWidth={1.5}/>;
        })}

        {/* Labels graduations */}
        {[{v:0,l:"0"},{v:50,l:"50"},{v:100,l:"100"}].map(({v,l})=>{
          const a = Math.PI + Math.PI*(v/100);
          const x = CX + (R+24)*Math.cos(a), y = CY + (R+24)*Math.sin(a);
          return <text key={v} x={x} y={y} textAnchor="middle" dominantBaseline="middle"
            fill="#9CAFC8" fontSize={9}>{l}</text>;
        })}

        {/* Aiguille */}
        <line x1={CX} y1={CY} x2={nx} y2={ny}
          stroke="#002147" strokeWidth={3} strokeLinecap="round"
          style={{transition:"all .8s ease"}}/>
        <circle cx={CX} cy={CY} r={7} fill="#002147"/>
        <circle cx={CX} cy={CY} r={4} fill="#fff"/>

        {/* Score central */}
        <text x={CX} y={CY - 14} textAnchor="middle"
          fill={color} fontSize={38} fontWeight={800}
          fontFamily="'Space Grotesk',sans-serif"
          style={{transition:"fill .4s"}}>
          {score}
        </text>
        <text x={CX} y={CY + 8} textAnchor="middle" fill="#9CAFC8" fontSize={12}>/100</text>

        {/* Labels extrÃªmes */}
        <text x={18} y={CY+20} textAnchor="middle" fill="#EF4444" fontSize={9} fontWeight={600}>Faible</text>
        <text x={222} y={CY+20} textAnchor="middle" fill="#22C55E" fontSize={9} fontWeight={600}>Optimal</text>

        {/* Badge niveau */}
        <rect x={CX-32} y={CY+18} width={64} height={18} rx={9}
          fill={color} opacity={0.15}/>
        <text x={CX} y={CY+29} textAnchor="middle"
          fill={color} fontSize={10} fontWeight={700}>
          {label}
        </text>
      </svg>
    </div>
  );
};

// â”€â”€ SKELETON OVERLAY (Canvas HTML5 sur vidÃ©o) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
// Simule les points MediaPipe sur la vidÃ©o et colore les articulations
const SkeletonOverlay = ({videoURL}) => {
  const videoRef = useRef(null);
  const canvasRef = useRef(null);
  const animRef = useRef(null);
  const [playing, setPlaying] = useState(false);

  // Points simulÃ©s MediaPipe (normalisÃ©s 0-1) pour une marche type
  // [hip, knee, ankle, shoulder] G et D
  const getPoseAtTime = (t) => {
    const phase = (t * 1.2) % (2 * Math.PI);
    return {
      // CÃ´tÃ© gauche
      lHip:   {x:0.42, y:0.42},
      lKnee:  {x:0.41 + 0.03*Math.sin(phase),     y:0.61 + 0.02*Math.sin(phase)},
      lAnkle: {x:0.40 + 0.06*Math.sin(phase+0.5), y:0.80},
      lToe:   {x:0.38 + 0.08*Math.sin(phase+0.8), y:0.88},
      // CÃ´tÃ© droit
      rHip:   {x:0.58, y:0.42},
      rKnee:  {x:0.59 + 0.03*Math.sin(phase+Math.PI),     y:0.61 + 0.02*Math.sin(phase+Math.PI)},
      rAnkle: {x:0.60 + 0.06*Math.sin(phase+Math.PI+0.5), y:0.80},
      rToe:   {x:0.62 + 0.08*Math.sin(phase+Math.PI+0.8), y:0.88},
      // Tronc
      lShoulder:{x:0.40, y:0.25}, rShoulder:{x:0.60, y:0.25},
      neck:     {x:0.50, y:0.18},
    };
  };

  // Calcul angle 3 points â†’ couleur
  const getJointColor = (a, b, c, idealMin, idealMax) => {
    const ang = (p1, p2, p3) => {
      const v1 = {x:p1.x-p2.x, y:p1.y-p2.y};
      const v2 = {x:p3.x-p2.x, y:p3.y-p2.y};
      const dot = v1.x*v2.x + v1.y*v2.y;
      const mag = Math.sqrt((v1.x**2+v1.y**2)) * Math.sqrt((v2.x**2+v2.y**2));
      return (Math.acos(Math.max(-1,Math.min(1,dot/mag))) * 180/Math.PI);
    };
    const deg = ang(a,b,c);
    if(deg >= idealMin && deg <= idealMax) return "#22C55E";
    if(deg >= idealMin-15 && deg <= idealMax+15) return "#F97316";
    return "#EF4444";
  };

  const drawSkeleton = useCallback(() => {
    const canvas = canvasRef.current;
    const video  = videoRef.current;
    if(!canvas) return;
    const ctx = canvas.getContext("2d");
    const W = canvas.width, H = canvas.height;
    ctx.clearRect(0,0,W,H);

    const t = video?.currentTime ?? (Date.now()/1000);
    const pts = getPoseAtTime(t);

    const px = (p) => ({x: p.x*W, y: p.y*H});

    // Connexions
    const connections = [
      ["lShoulder","rShoulder"],["lShoulder","lHip"],["rShoulder","rHip"],
      ["lHip","rHip"],
      ["lHip","lKnee"],["lKnee","lAnkle"],["lAnkle","lToe"],
      ["rHip","rKnee"],["rKnee","rAnkle"],["rAnkle","rToe"],
      ["lShoulder","neck"],["rShoulder","neck"],
    ];
    connections.forEach(([a,b])=>{
      const pa=px(pts[a]), pb=px(pts[b]);
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.moveTo(pa.x,pa.y); ctx.lineTo(pb.x,pb.y);
      ctx.strokeStyle="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)"; ctx.lineWidth=2;
      ctx.stroke();
    });

    // Articulations colorÃ©es
    const joints = [
      {name:"lHip",   p:pts.lHip,   a:pts.lShoulder, c:pts.lKnee,   min:150, max:180},
      {name:"lKnee",  p:pts.lKnee,  a:pts.lHip,      c:pts.lAnkle,  min:140, max:180},
      {name:"lAnkle", p:pts.lAnkle, a:pts.lKnee,     c:pts.lToe,    min:70,  max:110},
      {name:"rHip",   p:pts.rHip,   a:pts.rShoulder, c:pts.rKnee,   min:150, max:180},
      {name:"rKnee",  p:pts.rKnee,  a:pts.rHip,      c:pts.rAnkle,  min:140, max:180},
      {name:"rAnkle", p:pts.rAnkle, a:pts.rKnee,     c:pts.rToe,    min:70,  max:110},
    ];
    joints.forEach(({p,a,c,min,max,name})=>{
      const color = getJointColor(a,p,c,min,max);
      const {x,y} = px(p);
      // Halo lumineux
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.arc(x,y,11,0,2*Math.PI);
      ctx.fillStyle = color+"33"; ctx.fill();
      // Point
      ctx.beginPath();
      ctx.arc(x,y,6,0,2*Math.PI);
      ctx.fillStyle = color; ctx.fill();
      ctx.strokeStyle="#fff"; ctx.lineWidth=1.5; ctx.stroke();
    });

    // Autres points (neutres)
    ["neck","lShoulder","rShoulder","lToe","rToe"].forEach(k=>{
      const {x,y}=px(pts[k]);
      ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(x,y,4,0,2*Math.PI);
      ctx.fillStyle="rgba(255,255,255,0.8)"; ctx.fill();
    });
  },[]);

  useEffect(()=>{
    const loop = () => { drawSkeleton(); animRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(loop); };
    animRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(loop);
    return ()=>cancelAnimationFrame(animRef.current);
  },[drawSkeleton]);

  const togglePlay = () => {
    const v = videoRef.current;
    if(!v) return;
    v.paused ? v.play() : v.pause();
    setPlaying(!v.paused);
  };

  return (
    <div style={{position:"relative",borderRadius:12,overflow:"hidden",background:"#0A0F1E",aspectRatio:"16/9"}}>
      {videoURL
        ? <video ref={videoRef} src={videoURL} style={{width:"100%",height:"100%",objectFit:"cover",display:"block"}} loop muted playsInline/>
        : <div style={{width:"100%",height:"100%",background:"linear-gradient(135deg,#0D1B3E,#1A2F5C)",display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",alignItems:"center",justifyContent:"center",gap:8}}>
            <span style={{fontSize:36}}>ðŸ¦´</span>
            <span style={{color:"rgba(255,255,255,.5)",fontSize:12}}>Chargez une vidÃ©o pour voir le squelette</span>
          </div>
      }
      <canvas ref={canvasRef} width={640} height={360}
        style={{position:"absolute",inset:0,width:"100%",height:"100%",pointerEvents:"none"}}/>
      {videoURL&&(
        <button onClick={togglePlay}
          style={{position:"absolute",bottom:10,left:10,background:"rgba(0,0,0,.55)",border:"none",borderRadius:8,
            padding:"6px 14px",color:"#fff",fontSize:12,cursor:"pointer",backdropFilter:"blur(4px)"}}>
          {playing?"â¸ Pause":"â–¶ Play"}
        </button>
      )}
      {/* LÃ©gende flottante */}
      <div style={{position:"absolute",top:8,right:8,display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",gap:4,background:"rgba(0,0,0,.55)",
        borderRadius:8,padding:"8px 10px",backdropFilter:"blur(4px)"}}>
        {[["Optimal","#22C55E"],["DÃ©viation","#F97316"],["Anomalie","#EF4444"]].map(([l,c])=>(
          <span key={l} style={{display:"flex",alignItems:"center",gap:6,fontSize:10,color:"rgba(255,255,255,.85)"}}>
            <span style={{width:8,height:8,borderRadius:"50%",background:c,flexShrink:0}}/>
            {l}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

// â”€â”€ GAIT PHASE TIMELINE HORIZONTALE â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
